7293,"uid":44323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"用卓羅，其實係水遁"},{"pid":"b803a5d889b636f07c1d0283974636163f3163c3","tid":2287293,"uid":209418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:36:56.000Z","msg":"佢噴之前駁咗街條消防水喉咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cf6b16eb445b6559c5e7e3cc864fef0a1a9dbc","tid":2287293,"uid":238920,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://pansci.asia/archives/104426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Farchives%2F104426&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3qnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=8e608f9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://pansci.asia/archives/104426</a><br />\n<br />\n把數字都代進去，得知水柱從水箭龜砲管中噴出的速率是每秒 825 公尺。給大家作為比較，一般消防隊的水管噴水速率是每秒 20~30 公尺（注9），現代的步槍子彈速度是每秒 1200 公尺，至於砲彈的速度則是介於每秒 800~1000 公尺之間，所以水箭龜的砲管是名副其實的大砲。<br />\n<br />\n但還有一個東西叫後作用力，從動量守恆： mv=MV，5 公斤的水球之於 85 公斤水箭龜本身，計算後我們可以得到水箭龜理論上會以每秒 48 公尺的速度向後飛，也就是時速 172.8 公里<br />\n<br />\n事實上他每一次似乎都好端端地承受這每秒 825 公尺的反作用力，所以我們下一個問題大概會是：水箭龜的腳底是產生出了多大的摩擦力抵銷了後作用力。"},{"pid":"d797650cccb955fc2fd6c2d8958eea95326c0c7d","tid":2287293,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"開咗仙人模式啊"},{"pid":"b21b3fbf3990acff83e3d880b681acd9a3490de7","tid":2287293,"uid":15739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:49:11.000Z","msg":"因為佢係警嫂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add1c0604fac85d73ef2556a58582a0c9c28e07d","tid":2287293,"uid":36116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"好似鋼鍊咁提取空氣中嘅氫同氧再合成噴水。如此類推，小火龍就直點著啲氫噴火。"},{"pid":"8065152335f411a397a0102bed5057ebd97b8114","tid":2287293,"uid":133319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"25pp"},{"pid":"0e4f6544d1565ae50a19d4f3b768a5f460bd16b2","tid":2287293,"uid